## What & why
The trace server's serialization/canonicalization/digest logic lives in Python
(weave.shared) and is reimplemented (not shared) by other-language SDKs (TS).
Divergence => different digests for the same object => broken refs/dedup. The
corpus freezes (input -> expected) examples as JSONL; every SDK ships a consumer
that asserts its impl reproduces each row.

## Contents
- conformance/{README.md,generate_fixtures.py,fixtures/*.jsonl}: the
